title: Obama vetoes defense bill in feud with GOP
text: Touching off a furious battle with Congress, President Obama vetoed the defense authorization bill Thursday in a dispute with Republican lawmakers over spending limits and the closing of the Guantanamo Bay detention facility. "I'm going to be sending it back to Congress and my message to them is very simple: ... ...
